                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-33-defend314 t18000219-33-punish200"></join>
               publicly whipped
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
